## Template Syntax Reference

### Variables
{% raw %}
- `{{ variable }}` - Output a variable
- `{{ var | filter }}` - Apply a filter
{% endraw %}

### Conditionals
```jinja
{% raw %}
{% if condition %}
  ...
{% elif other %}
  ...
{% else %}
  ...
{% endif %}
{% endraw %}
```

### Loops
```jinja
{% raw %}
{% for item in items %}
  {{ item }}
{% endfor %}
{% endraw %}
```

### Filters
- `| join(",")` - Join array with separator
- `| default("fallback")` - Provide default value
- `| upper`, `| lower` - Case conversion
- `| items` - Convert dict to key-value pairs
